thread.title: Joanne Johnson
thread.title_full: Country Attire Ltd. (www.countryattire.com) reviewed by Joanne Johnson

author: Joanne Johnson
title: Joanne Johnson
text: Ordered a Barbour jacket for my son but when arrived the style only had press studs and not a zip and quality wasn't as expected, was very thin, so ordered another one and it arrived the very next day, better quality and with zip. Also refund for first jacket was processed very quick.
